display="block"><![CDATA[\alpha (\alpha (x,g),h)=\alpha (x,gh)]]></fr:tex></fr:li></fr:ol><fr:p>Note: usually we write <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[x\cdot  g]]></fr:tex> instead of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\alpha (x,g)]]></fr:tex> when the action is unambiguous.</fr:p>
 
   
